extendedInfo.description: Official mobile website app for Katherine GlassCHT Spiritual Intuitive CounselorKatherine Glass comes from a lineage of psychic sensitives and healers. Born in the caul, long considered to be a sign of true psychic ability, she has been using her gifts to bring help and healing to others for over 20 years. She is a graduate of the Barbara Brennan School of Healing, and Sharon Turner's Awakenings Clairvoyant Program, and has trained at the Arthur Findlay College in Stansted, England. Psychic intuitive readings and mediumistic readings are given in person,or by telephone and on Skype.Katherine is the co-founder of the Healing Essence Center in Concord, MA
